    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable car for me and is still in really solid shape! It\u2019s super clean, drives smoothly, and has plenty of life left in it. Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out on a road trip, this beauty won\u2019t let you down. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused BMW E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example is paired with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains rigid with documented subframe reinforcement, and the high-pressure VANOS system has been serviced to ensure optimal cam timing. Suspension geometry is tight, benefiting from refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity and linear power delivery remain uncompromised.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Clean title. Maintenance records available. Minor exterior scuffs. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2018 BMW 330i xDrive that perfectly balances luxury and performance. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and is in reliable, road-ready condition. The Alpine White exterior remains vibrant and glossy; while there are a handful of minor rock chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel, the body is straight and free of any major dents. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and features Black SensaTec upholstery that shows virtually no wear, with firm bolsters and clean carpeting throughout. All premium features, including the power moonroof, heated front seats, and the iDrive infotainment system with integrated navigation, are fully operational. Under the hood, the 2.0L turbocharged engine runs smoothly, supported by a comprehensive service history. The most recent maintenance included a synthetic oil change, a fresh cabin air filter, and a multi-point inspection that confirmed the brakes and suspension are in solid shape. The tires currently sit at roughly 70% tread life. This car comes with two key fobs, the original owner's manuals, and a clean title in hand.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, representing a superior balance of performance and long-term value. This unit has undergone a rigorous inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and aesthetic refinement. Featuring a clean history and a well-preserved interior, it offers a dependable driving experience for the discerning owner. We invite you to experience the quality and sophistication of this exceptional offering firsthand.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and runs like a dream! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it\u2019s totally ready for a new home where it can hit the road again. It\u2019s the perfect balance of reliable and fun. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by and take it for a spin. I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
