    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s analog peak, powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is paired with a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a functional M-Variable differential lock. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a VANOS system refresh and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under load. The suspension features refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers for neutralized body roll. While the finish shows minor road-derived patina, the powertrain remains stout and delivers linear, high-revving performance. A true driver\u2019s car with sorted mechanicals.",
